Subject: [PATCH 7/7] modetest: Add pattern support for xilinx tiled formats in
 modetest

In modetest, implemented support of SMPTE and tiles patterns
generation for xilinx tile formats of YUV400, YUV420, YUV422
& YUV444 formats with 8/10/12 bpc

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [Xilinx specific]
Signed-off-by: Neel Gandhi <neel.gandhi@amd.com>
